    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "莉央にプロポーズする",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "choice_selection",
              "choices": [
                {
                  "text": "ご飯",
                  "route": []
                },
                {
                  "text": "お風呂",
                  "route": []
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_heart-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 300.0000051099
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-koh014.m4a",
              "text": "好きです\n俺と結婚して下さい",
              "startTime": 300.0000051099,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-rio012.m4a",
              "text": "何言ってるのよ\n今更そんな冗談……",
              "startTime": 303.8000051099,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-koh015.m4a",
              "text": "冗談じゃありません\n俺の莉央さんを好きな気持ちは\nあの頃から何一つ変わっていません",
              "startTime": 308.5333384433,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-koh016.m4a",
              "text": "俺と別れる時、莉央さんは言いましたよね\n「私よりももっとふさわしい人と\n幸せになって」と……",
              "startTime": 315.7666717766,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-koh017.m4a",
              "text": "俺はこの数年、莉央さんを一番近くで\n見てきました。莉央さんのそばにいて\n自分の気持ちを考え続けて、確信したんです",
              "startTime": 325.7000152825,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-koh018.m4a",
              "text": "やっぱり俺は莉央さんが好きです\n莉央さん以外の人と一緒になっても\n俺は幸せになんかなれません",
              "startTime": 336.6000152825,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-rio013.m4a",
              "text": "でも、私は恋愛と仕事を秤にかけて\n仕事を選ぶような人間よ\nそんな私と付き合っても不幸になるだけよ",
              "startTime": 345.3666819492,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-koh019.m4a",
              "text": "どうして恋と仕事のどちらかを\n選ぼうとするんですか\nどちらかを諦める必要なんてありません",
              "startTime": 356.1333486158,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-koh020.m4a",
              "text": "今の俺は新人の頃とは違います\nあの頃は未熟で、何も出来なかったけど……\n今の俺なら仕事でも莉央さんを支えられます",
              "startTime": 363.3666819492,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-koh021.m4a",
              "text": "どちらかを諦めなくても、俺が恋と仕事の\n両方で莉央さんを幸せにしてみせます\nだから、俺を信じて下さい！",
              "startTime": 374.8666819492,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-rio014.m4a",
              "text": "でも、私は貴方より年上で、可愛くもなくて\n仕事人間で、恋愛が下手で……\n……こんな私で本当にいいの？",
              "startTime": 384.1666778802,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-koh022.m4a",
              "text": "莉央さんがいいんです\n好きです。俺と結婚して下さい",
              "startTime": 400.3333445469,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-rio015.m4a",
              "text": "……ありがとう\n私も貴方が大好きよ",
              "startTime": 406.2999908684,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 413.333328247
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": null,
              "speakerName": "",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": null,
              "text": "――数ヶ月後",
              "startTime": 414.1666615803,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
                  "delay": 2233.3332856999846
                },
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 1135.2030437000167
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 415.2666656493
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-koh023.m4a",
              "text": "ただいま～",
              "startTime": 416.0999990063,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-rio016.m4a",
              "text": "お帰りなさい。お仕事お疲れ様\nご飯にする？　お風呂にする？\nそれとも私？",
              "startTime": 417.566686018,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-rio017.m4a",
              "text": "……ちょっと、何ニヤニヤしてるのよ",
              "startTime": 426.9667022941,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-koh024.m4a",
              "text": "いや、昔は恥ずかしがって言えなかったのに\n随分慣れたなと思って",
              "startTime": 430.4667043286,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-rio018.m4a",
              "text": "昔のことは言わないで！\n新婚らしくしようと\n私なりに頑張ってるんだから",
              "startTime": 436.7333709953,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-rio019.m4a",
              "text": "来週から海外出張でしょ？\nだから今のうちに新婚気分を満喫しなきゃ",
              "startTime": 443.1666900871,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-rio020.m4a",
              "text": "私は仕事も恋愛も\n充実させるって決めたんだから",
              "startTime": 449.5333567538,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-rio021.m4a",
              "text": "それで、どうするの？\nご飯にする？　お風呂にする？\nそれとも私？",
              "startTime": 453.6333486158,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 460.6610130865
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-koh025.m4a",
              "text": "そうですね……じゃあ、俺は……",
              "startTime": 462.6333506504,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 5766.644263300009
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 468.2666432698
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-rio022.m4a",
              "text": "それで、どうしてこうなったのかしら？",
              "startTime": 469.1333201329,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-koh026.m4a",
              "text": "だって、莉央さんからあんな風に迫られて\nどれか一つになんて\n決められる訳ないじゃないですか",
              "startTime": 473.1666575353,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
                  "delay": 0
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-koh027.m4a",
              "text": "だから、ご飯とお風呂と莉央さん\n全部もらうことにしたんです",
              "startTime": 481.0666392248,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 3100.0315108000223
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-rio023.m4a",
              "text": "全部って……\nこの状況で『お風呂』と『私』は分かるけど\n『ご飯』はどこに行ったのよ",
              "startTime": 488.2332875809,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
                  "delay": 0
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-rio024.m4a",
              "text": "……もしかして私\n今から貴方に食べられちゃうのかしら？",
              "startTime": 496.9999339026,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 166.73683300001585
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-koh028.m4a",
              "text": "莉央さん……凄く綺麗です……",
              "startTime": 504.3666127762,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 0
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-rio025.m4a",
              "text": "ちょ、ちょっと、じろじろ見ないでよ\n恥ずかしいじゃない",
              "startTime": 508.0332794429,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 0
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-koh029.m4a",
              "text": "すみません。でも照れる莉央さんも\n可愛いです。こんなに素敵な女性と\n結婚出来て、俺は世界一の幸せ者です",
              "startTime": 512.9999461096,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_01-rio026.m4a",
              "text": "……世界一幸せなのはお互い様よ",
              "startTime": 524.3332672359,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_chu-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 16166.7012291
                },
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 16166.7012291
                },
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 10366.736833099934
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "仕事のパートナーとして莉央について行く",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 543.9999542477
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
